### **3. 40_LogToneScanner**  
**Description:**  
Scans logs to detect anomalies, frequent lines, and abnormal tone shifts (errors/warnings bursts).

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogToneScanner - Log Frequency & Spike Analyzer

LogToneScanner helps identify spikes, noise, or critical messages that repeat often or cluster unexpectedly.

## Features
- Burst detection  
- Keyword grouping  
- Frequency summary  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/40_LogToneScanner.git
cd 40_LogToneScanner
python analyze.py logs/app.log
